data.description: Built real estate apps with Flutter, integrating APIs, Google Maps, and Firebase (Crashlytics, Analytics). Designed responsive UI from Figma, supporting localization for multilingual users. Used clean architecture and Bloc for maintainable, scalable code. Managed tasks with Jira and collaborated via Slack for efficient remote work.

Enhanced user and delivery apps and developed a new vendor app using Flutter. Implemented streams for real-time data, improving app responsiveness. Applied MVVM architecture with Provider for modular code. Ensured app reliability through testing and bug fixes. Added features with Branch.io for deep linking and Sentry for error tracking.

Developed 5+ mobile apps using Flutter. Collaborated with backend, ML, DevOps, and design teams for feature delivery. Wrote technical documentation in Markdown to aid onboarding. Managed tasks with ClickUp and Notion for timely feature delivery.
Completed mandatory military service, developing discipline, leadership, and teamwork skills. Managed responsibilities under pressure while maintaining commitment to personal and professional growth.

Gained hands-on experience in Flutter, focusing on state management, API integration, and local storage. Assisted in developing mobile applications, enhancing skills in Dart and app architecture. Contributed to team projects, learning agile workflows and version control with Git.

Developed mobile applications for educational and health sectors. Integrated Paymob payment gateway for secure in-app transactions. Fixed bugs related to in-app purchases and Apple Push Notification Service. Collaborated with clients to deliver tailored solutions, meeting specific requirements.

Developed solutions using C/C++, Java, and Python, focusing on data structures and algorithms. Optimized code for computational efficiency in algorithmic challenges. Collaborated with senior engineers to apply data handling techniques in real-world projects.

Faculty of Computers and Artificial Intelligence. Studied Mobile Application Development, Data Structures, Algorithms, and Software Engineering. Graduation Project: Augmented Reality application using Flutter and Unity 3D (A Grade).
